				</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>
			<dt class='gallery-icon '>
				<a href='http://activehistory.ca/papers/history-paper-3/figure-6/'><img width="1" height="1" src="http://activehistory.ca/wp-content/uploads/2010/01/Figure-6.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail" alt="" aria-describedby="gallery-3-710" data-attachment-id="710" data-permalink="http://activehistory.ca/papers/history-paper-3/figure-6/" data-orig-file="http://activehistory.ca/wp-content/uploads/2010/01/Figure-6.jpg" data-orig-size="" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="[]" data-image-title="Figure 6" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="http://activehistory.ca/wp-content/uploads/2010/01/Figure-6.jpg" data-large-file="http://activehistory.ca/wp-content/uploads/2010/01/Figure-6.jpg" /></a>
			</dt>
				<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-3-710'>
				Figure 6: General Amir Machmud addressing a meeting prior to the “act of free choice,” 1969, from Suyanto Hadinoto, ed., <em>25 Tahun Trikora [25 Years of Trikora]</em> (Jakarta: n.p., [1988]).
				</dd></dl><br style="clear: both" /><dl class='gallery-item'>
			<dt class='gallery-icon '>
				<a href='http://activehistory.ca/papers/history-paper-3/figure-7/'><img width="1" height="1" src="http://activehistory.ca/wp-content/uploads/2010/01/Figure-7.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail" alt="" aria-describedby="gallery-3-711" data-attachment-id="711" data-permalink="http://activehistory.ca/papers/history-paper-3/figure-7/" data-orig-file="http://activehistory.ca/wp-content/uploads/2010/01/Figure-7.jpg" data-orig-size="" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="[]" data-image-title="Figure 7" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="http://activehistory.ca/wp-content/uploads/2010/01/Figure-7.jpg" data-large-file="http://activehistory.ca/wp-content/uploads/2010/01/Figure-7.jpg" /></a>
			</dt>
				<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-3-711'>
				Figure 7: Indonesian poster, photograph from <em>Api Perjuangan Pembebasan Irian Barat</em> (Jakarta : Yayasan Badan Kontak Keluarga Besar Perintis Irian Barat, 1986).
				</dd></dl>
			<br style='clear: both' />
		</div>
</p>
